    <section class="intro">
        <div class="inner tight">
            <main>
                    <h1>
                        On the brink
                    </h1>
                                    <p class="strapline">
                        The wildcat is one of our rarest and most threatened mammals.
                    </p>

                <p>Once widespread, wildcats are now on the brink of extinction in Scotland.</p>
<p>A sad history of habitat loss, persecution and, more recently, breeding with domestic cats, has forced the Highland Tiger to a point where the population is no longer viable. </p>
<p>Without urgent action, wildcats will be lost forever from Britain.</p>
<p><img style="float: left;" src="/media/sbrn3cyb/gordon-buchanan.jpg?width=163&amp;height=184&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="163" height="184"></p>
<p> </p>
<p><em>“The thought of never having the chance to film or photograph the iconic wildcat in the Scottish highlands is a deeply saddening thought. We must value this incredible species and do everything we can to ensure its survival” </em></p>
<p><strong>Gordon Buchanan, wildlife filmmaker and presenter</strong></p>
<p> </p>
